        "baseRefName": "master",
        "body": "This PR redefines the Weyl group of a root pairing as the subgroup of automorphisms generated by reflection morphisms. The new definition is isomorphic to the old one, by faithfulness of the weight space representation, but we also get a natural coweight space representation and permutation representation on roots.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n[![Open in Gitpod](https://gitpod.io/button/open-in-gitpod.svg)](https://gitpod.io/from-referrer/)\r\n",
        "changedFiles": 4,
